<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-1943] RFC5424 Layout ignores event prefix</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1943</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In RFC5424Layout the mdcPrefix should add a prefix value to ThreadContext values only. Instead it adds the prefix to all attributes. The eventPrefix should be added to attributes that are not ThreadContext attributes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
